{"tid":2210213,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【大學洗太平地】葉蔭聰：更多比我低調的偏「黃」學者都被大學踢走。","createTime":"2020-09-20T08:53:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-21T13:39:28.000Z","uid":209657,"like":60,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"ba46ca6c2767b7e1a23d394690aee8a4817e0044","tid":2210213,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T08:53:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2020/09/%E8%91%89%E8%94%AD%E8%81%B0-20200918215724_2e59.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2020%2F09%2F%25E8%2591%2589%25E8%2594%25AD%25E8%2581%25B0-20200918215724_2e59.jpg&h=a4353059&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n繼戴耀廷、邵家臻後，再有活躍政治的學者被大學「踢走」，這次是葉蔭聰。葉蔭聰這名字未必人人熟識。他是嶺南大學文化研究系助理教授，亦是獨立媒體創辦人之一，不時在報章寫時事評論文章批評政府，令人質疑他被踢走，是出於政治原因。<br />\n<br />\n相較於戴、邵二人，葉蔭聰低調得多。不過他說，近年很多比他更低調的偏「黃」學者都被大學踢走。大學正以一種看來相當合符程序的低調方式，靜悄悄地清洗太平地。<br />\n<br />\n葉蔭聰在嶺大任教18年，最初是授課導師，後來受聘為助理教授，6年前轉為終身合約制(tenure track)，任期今年8月完結，需要申請實任(substantiation)，成功申請才能獲得終身教席。他上月初被通知申請被拒，學校只給他一年臨時合約，明年8月結束。<br />\n<br />\n葉蔭聰經常在報章發表時事評論，他也心知他的社會參與會惹來高層不喜歡，故本來對成功申請就不感樂觀。他實任被拒，最感驚訝的是文化研究系印籍系主任寧蒂珠(Tejaswini Niranjana)，「佢到而家都完全唔明白，唔明上面啲人咁決定。」<br />\n<br />\n那一直以來有否感受到甚麼壓力？葉蔭聰說，早幾年曾被上頭告訴他「唔好寫咁多無聊嘢（時事評論）」，他說，當下的確有點不高興，但事後回想，對方未必是惡意，或想給他政治壓力，可能只是好心提醒。"},{"pid":"6c5c387e39846bd1508d401a705b46b0864e74fd","tid":2210213,"uid":82640,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T08:55:51.000Z","msg":"世界級 Tejaswini Niranjana 都趕走<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4117ee105179ff65d1075a4b79c42a024307222d","tid":2210213,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T08:56:46.000Z","msg":"篇文好長<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/33931/%E8%91%89%E8%94%AD%E8%81%B0-%E5%B6%BA%E5%8D%97%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8-33931/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F33931%2F%25E8%2591%2589%25E8%2594%25AD%25E8%2581%25B0-%25E5%25B6%25BA%25E5%258D%2597%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8-33931%2F&d=eCiXx0TsV7ZnsYjNRM2OmpR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=51238817\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/33931/%E8%91%89%E8%94%AD%E8%81%B0-%E5%B6%BA%E5%8D%97%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8-33931/</a>"},{"pid":"c50b5bbedbdfe9ff02703f7b121206ab1904d2a3","tid":2210213,"uid":209657,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T08:58:09.000Z","msg":"「大學嘅politics唔係你哋媒體所想像嘅politics，你哋嘅係好過度簡化。喺大學入面，嗰種好戲劇性嘅打壓，其實好少發生。」<br />\n<br />\n他指的戲劇性打壓，例如是戴耀廷被解僱及2015年陳文敏事件，是將「超乎尋常」的手段用得特別露骨。但這種戲劇性的打壓，其實不常見。<br />\n<br />\n大部分情況，其實一點都不戲劇性。他舉例，例如邵家臻不獲續約，做法其實很平常，在任何大學都會發生，是因為邵的議員身份才顯得戲劇性，如果是個較低調的「黃學者」，事情一樣會發生，但就不會構成新聞。<br />\n<br />\n他舉例，一個港大學者朋友，在該學系中專做香港研究，也被踢走，「我哋覺得完全唔合理，但呢啲唔會出到新聞，連佢自己都唔知點將自己故仔講畀媒體聽。你話裡面背後有冇politics呢，我覺得係有。因為係人睇佢啲文都知佢係黃。」雖然，背後是否只是涉及黃藍的因素，葉覺得可能很複雜。"},{"pid":"fb7c454c9721d0036a08ba39ff3c49e155ee52bd","tid":2210213,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T08:58:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"674416d18ec62e0773f3a4143baa4117446b2cb7","tid":2210213,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T08:59:43.000Z","msg":"全面清洗"},{"pid":"4fc6a7f3b3d1e31edc0ad441e701910312e05ab3","tid":2210213,"uid":11809,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T09:00:04.000Z","msg":"學術自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0943e1773a45049c33a268e3e0789d55b1473acd","tid":2210213,"uid":209657,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T09:01:45.000Z","msg":"要踢走一個學者，可以有很多正當理由包裝。大學對教研人員研究出版方面的要求與日俱增，亦有更多理由可以踢走一個人，可以是他有否足夠學術期刊文章，就算夠又是否夠國際級等等。有時候，就會混雜政治在其中，<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">早幾日先聽到某校嘅高層，成日要整人文學科學系，佢會話『你個學系都唔係學問嚟嘅，淨係教人點示威遊行。』</span><br />\n<br />\n整個系統運作時，會跟足各樣程序，有看來正當的理由。「大學裡面嘅政治係咁。唔係咁清晰好似做大戲大花面咁，有個人代表西環嚟治校，唔係咁，亦唔需要係咁。」打壓並不是透過舞台上的大花臉反派角色，而是透過看來依足程序的人事制度。"},{"pid":"fe0620bbb2731feca88dd6015ed76046e2ca121a","tid":2210213,"uid":209657,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T09:05:40.000Z","msg":"港大法律系副教授戴耀廷、浸大社工系講師邵家臻、浸大政治及國際關系學系前助理教授兼教職員工會主席黃偉國、嶺大中文系前助理教授陳雲，這幾個人名，都是近年被解僱或不獲續約的偏黃學者。但在肉眼可見的冰山下，還有更多不為人知的個案。葉蔭聰說，很多未必為人熟悉偏黃學者都被踢走，「有啲人比我更低調。連佢自己都搞唔清畀人踢走嘅原因係咩。」<br />\n<br />\n而令他感到有點可悲的是，這些尋常被踢走故事，未必得到同行的同情。他舉例，當年黃偉國在浸大被踢走，有些他認為屬於偏黃的同行，也覺得純粹是因為黃學術水平不足而被踢走。<br />\n<br />\n葉蔭聰身處整個局勢之中，自言難以超然地評估趨勢是否近年急速惡化。不過他說感覺到隨著整個政治氣氛轉變，事實上亦看到有朋友相繼遇到類似情況，感覺上是較以往嚴重。"},{"pid":"ff9ec755266a8c83490468d9d6dae88d8a0ccba8","tid":2210213,"uid":209657,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T09:08:58.000Z","msg":"「大掃除」之後，葉蔭聰覺得，很多政治上偏黃的學者，都會轉趨低調。<br />\n「行內有個潛規則，你拎tenure（終身合約）之前，最好唔好喺出面講咁多嘢。我有個朋友直頭同我講，話佢連Facebook都唔寫了。」<br />\n<br />\n有研究題目圍繞香港社會、政治事件的學者朋友，比他更為低調，也對於取得終身教席感到悲觀，透露可能考慮轉到海外發展，即使最後留港的話，亦會轉得更低調。葉蔭聰說，這樣的例子不是孤例，事實上寫評論的學者亦已一直減少。<br />\n<br />\n這種「洗太平地」會否陸續有來？他認為應該會，但當學者轉趨低調後，或者可以成功隱身，免被清洗。"},{"pid":"5cb5006c3501a925fc8aa1d2d791c63473628a43","tid":2210213,"uid":275877,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T09:11:28.000Z","msg":"教育界大清洗，全部變晒洗腦愛支教育"},{"pid":"a50d3cd9c0ad59db3f0ee2dad5fbd4d2decb04a5","tid":2210213,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T09:14:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d66701b0afc47fae9065630d9bc8c41abf51245","tid":2210213,"uid":273218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T09:14:34.000Z","msg":"唔好比位對方入"},{"pid":"6e7157685b1807d793739608996d015458d6ee13","tid":2210213,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T09:21:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9686a9866abc6a540d9c035c8eeffb8eb7bf15e3","tid":2210213,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T09:27:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb055f4c9fb0b84c4aafb621a73afcaeb15fc5af","tid":2210213,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T09:37:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42e858084868ebe8c50f808a137f9229615b5330","tid":2210213,"uid":331973,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T09:41:06.000Z","msg":"幾年前就洗緊，只係而家浮面，加速<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/threat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"413a98943cfff59ab02066787959d5aae17654f7","tid":2210213,"uid":34222,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T09:48:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一直都洗緊<br />\n以前冇人理唔係好覺<br />\n大學美其名話唔續約<br />\n其實咪又係政治原因炒9人<br />\n人文學科d學者係香港不嬲都比人睇低"},{"pid":"a05bef74a50c18279481d569908a8bee6ebd8ca0","tid":2210213,"uid":76382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T09:49:21.000Z","msg":"推上熱門 等多啲人關注<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"578f40f3ff9516b1556806675270d24deda6a727","tid":2210213,"uid":61280,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T09:54:45.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">文人多大話，教畜多犬儒<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！！！</span></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"3f12124e3d3106628d66c574963fdaf4742eeeea","tid":2210213,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T09:58:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bb1d6e97e5f63afd4e585d764580bbe9c9c4aa2","tid":2210213,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T10:09:43.000Z","msg":"&quot;6年前轉為終身合約制(tenure track)&quot;<br />\n<br />\nD記者係咪唔識分tenured同tenure track? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e825188e0c7245539267d8d9ab5419ef3c32f941","tid":2210213,"uid":66324,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"0943e1773a45049c33a268e3e0789d55b1473acd","tid":2210213,"uid":209657,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T09:01:45.000Z","msg":"要踢走一個學者，可以有很多正當理由包裝。大學對教研人員研究出版方面的要求與日俱增，亦有更多理由可以踢走一個人，可以是他有否足夠學術期刊文章，就算夠又是否夠國際級等等。有時候，就會混雜政治在其中，<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">早幾日先聽到某校嘅高層，成日要整人文學科學系，佢會話『你個學系都唔係學問嚟嘅，淨係教人點示威遊行。』</span><br />\n<br />\n整個系統運作時，會跟足各樣程序，有看來正當的理由。「大學裡面嘅政治係咁。唔係咁清晰好似做大戲大花面咁，有個人代表西環嚟治校，唔係咁，亦唔需要係咁。」打壓並不是透過舞台上的大花臉反派角色，而是透過看來依足程序的人事制度。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T10:11:15.000Z","msg":"香港D大學一向都想整頓D唔搵食出紙少的學系架啦, 要衝排名呀ma <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff6e6c4fcf151de75ca1cd66e9b8e013b9fd5738","tid":2210213,"uid":235152,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T10:14:51.000Z","msg":"排名 年年跌唔係冇原因"},{"pid":"18aefae10f4ccda35b69d20be5974443d99e8b82","tid":2210213,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff6e6c4fcf151de75ca1cd66e9b8e013b9fd5738","tid":2210213,"uid":235152,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T10:14:51.000Z","msg":"排名 年年跌唔係冇原因"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T10:20:53.000Z","msg":"XGDX無利用價值之後就要壓到連二本都不如 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"184acb090572cecf602fbd79bc1e86c3497648b7","tid":2210213,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff6e6c4fc